_sText:
Quick Gun-Game map series.

GG_03 is the third map in my quick-map-making series.

The goal of this series is to produce as many completed maps as possible, mainly for experience.

The best will be re-textured, re-built and re-released.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Description: A medium sized map with long lines of sight, and interesting cover opportunities.

Theme: Tank-Trap like cover spots.

Size: Medium

Max Players: 44

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

At 7.5MB .bz2 is recommended.

Please tell me what you think.
